{
  "id": "gedit_env_file_sanitize",
  "app": "gedit",
  "task": "/home/user/Documents/app.env currently has 12 lines (settings, secrets, and one blank line):\n\n```\nAPP_NAME=myapp\nAPP_ENV=production\nDB_PASSWORD=s3cret_p4ss\nHOST=127.0.0.1\nPORT=8080\nAPI_SECRET=abc123xyz\nDEBUG=false\nJWT_TOKEN=ey.fake.jwt\nTIMEOUT=30\nAUTH_TOKEN=t0k3n\nLOG_LEVEL=info\n(blank line)\n```\n\nSanitize the file so that:\n- Every line whose KEY contains `PASSWORD`, `SECRET`, or `TOKEN` is removed (i.e. `DB_PASSWORD`, `API_SECRET`, `JWT_TOKEN`, `AUTH_TOKEN` are all gone).\n- The blank line is removed.\n- Every remaining value is wrapped in double quotes (e.g. `APP_NAME=\"myapp\"`, `PORT=\"8080\"`).\n- The last line (line 8) is exactly the comment `# Sanitized for production`.\n\nThe final file must have exactly 8 lines (7 sanitized settings + 1 trailing comment).",
  "env": {
    "files": [
      {
        "filename": "app.env",
        "sandbox_path": "/home/user/Documents/app.env"
      }
    ]
  },
  "verification": [
    {
      "command": "check-file-exists /home/user/Documents/app.env",
      "key": "exists",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "app.env still exists"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-line-count /home/user/Documents/app.env 8",
      "key": "matches",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "File has exactly 8 lines"
    },
    {
      "command": "file-content /home/user/Documents/app.env",
      "eval": "'PASSWORD' not in result.get('content', '')",
      "description": "No PASSWORD lines remain"
    },
    {
      "command": "file-content /home/user/Documents/app.env",
      "eval": "'SECRET' not in result.get('content', '')",
      "description": "No SECRET lines remain"
    },
    {
      "command": "file-content /home/user/Documents/app.env",
      "eval": "'TOKEN' not in result.get('content', '')",
      "description": "No TOKEN lines remain"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"APP_NAME=\\\"myapp\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "APP_NAME value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"APP_ENV=\\\"production\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "APP_ENV value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"HOST=\\\"127.0.0.1\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "HOST value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"PORT=\\\"8080\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "PORT value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"DEBUG=\\\"false\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "DEBUG value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"TIMEOUT=\\\"30\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
      "description": "TIMEOUT value is quoted"
    },
    {
      "command": "check-file-contains /home/user/Documents/app.env \"LOG_LEVEL=\\\"info\\\"\"",
      "key": "contains",
      "expected": true,
